casebody.data:
WELLS FARGO BANK, N.A., AS TRUSTEE, FOR CARRINGTON MORTGAGE LOAN TRUST, etc., Plaintiff
v.
Anthony CZYZ and Catherine Czyz, Defendants-Appellants. M-448 September Term 2018
080644 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 11, 2019

ORDER

This matter having been duly presented to the Court on defendants' appeal as of right from the judgment of the Superior Court, Appellate Division in A-000611-17, and the Court having determined that the matter does not raise a substantial constitutional question under Rule 2:2-1(a)(1) and the applicable case law;

It is ORDERED that the appeal is dismissed on the Court's own motion.
